---
/**
 * Importanța Albinelor - BEE112
 *
 * BMAD Phase 4: Secondary pages
 * Phase 9: Content Freeze ACTIVE - text is LOCKED
 *
 * Source of truth: .bmad/content/phase4-importanta-albinelor.md
